  "body": "<!--NOTE: -->\r\n<!--- General questions should go to the discord chat instead of the issue tracker.-->\r\n\r\n**Describe the bug**\r\n\r\nValidator monitor for altair is not able to differentiate between missed head and inclusion distance > 1. We need to be aware of the difference to optimize performance.\r\n\r\n**Expected behavior**\r\n\r\nValidator monitor should report\r\n- head bit is set (correct head + fast inclusion)\r\n- head is correct\r\n- exact inclusion distance\r\n\r\nYou should check Lighthouse code or / and reach out to them to see how they adapted the validator monitor for post altair",
